sudoku.si
Class NullConfig

java.lang.Object
  sudoku.si.Config
      sudoku.si.NullConfig

public class NullConfig
extends Config

A "Null Object" pattern instance. The root Config when traversing from parent to parent peters out. System properties are the configuration points of last resort that gets on this Config object return.
